  • Method Details

    • buildAndRegister

      @NotNull @NotNull GraphUniverse buildAndRegister(@NotNull @NotNull Identifier universeId)
      Builds and registers the GraphUniverse described by this builder.

      Right before each GraphUniverse is built, GraphLib invokes all the UniverseModifierRegistry.Modify registered for the given universe id as well as each registered UniverseModifierRegistry.ModifyAll. This allows mods to register decoders and detectors for other mods' universes.

      Parameters:
      universeId - the unique id of the GraphUniverse to be built.
      Returns:
      the newly created GraphUniverse.

    • decoder

      @Contract("_, _ -> this") @NotNull @NotNull GraphUniverse.Builder decoder(@NotNull @NotNull Identifier typeId, @NotNull @NotNull BlockNodeDecoder decoder)
      Registers a BlockNodeDecoder for the given block node type id.

      The identifier under which the decoder is registered corresponds to the one returned by the associated block node's BlockNode.getTypeId().

      Parameters:
      typeId - the type id of the block node the decoder is being registered for.
      decoder - the block node decoder responsible for decoding the associated type of block node.
      Returns:
      this builder for call chaining.
